00:28:46.280 --> 00:28:52.599
which is great, especially if, like I said, if you're sharing this server,

00:28:52.599 --> 00:28:56.119
this Flickr cluster, and also if you're new to Spark,

00:28:56.920 --> 00:29:00.040
you can start without any settings and in any way.

00:29:01.000 --> 00:29:06.520
You can start without any settings and in a data lake for using Yarn client.

