00:30:54.520 --> 00:30:57.239
Or I do what we talked about in option two,

00:30:57.239 --> 00:31:01.560
essentially load into our memory and then put it in Spark, which is what I'm doing here.

00:31:01.560 --> 00:31:05.160
So I'm going to read it into memory using read R.

