The way that Spark VR approached this has helped us to be able to use Spark VR in a

00:45:31.719 --> 00:45:33.879
very effective way.

00:45:33.879 --> 00:45:39.159
And the other thing that tells me is the fact that we're having webinars and really promoting

00:45:39.159 --> 00:45:44.439
it and also developing it, it's just supposed to show that our commitment to make it even

00:45:44.439 --> 00:45:49.000
better for everyone, I think that says a lot as well.

